metadata.name: first jump 2023 #1/23
metadata.description:
I've been sick to bed at the beginning of the year, so I'm late celebrating.  
But now that I'm finally cured of my illness, there's nothing to be afraid of.  
No more sickness or injury! I'll jump and leap like a rabbit all year long!

I wish you all a colorful and happy year 2023!!!
